<p class="">That will make a very short day. In addition to that there are Bills, which will reduce the time still more, and many hon. Members will want to attend Armistice services in their own constituencies. I wonder whether the right hon. Gentleman will consider it worth while taking any other business.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
