            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-8eaaf54d-c380-4494-b65c-08bd109711a2">
                Mr. George Griffiths
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-8eaaf54d-c380-4494-b65c-08bd109711a2" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
