        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-6a98928a-1a67-4702-9ab2-3d483a2aa9b0'>
            
<p class="">7.1 p.m.</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
